title: Mixtape Padalgal
subTitle: A comprehensive compilation of some of the most popular and beloved musical numbers from the year, played consecutively.

title: Kaala Bairavan
subTitle: Jogeshwari is the daughter of Dakshan who hates Shiva and worships Vishnu. When Dakshan forces Jogeshwari to marry, she rebels because of her dedication towards Bhairavan, a devout devotee of Shiva.

title: Veera Anjaneya
subTitle: Hanuman, son of Anjani and Kesari, is an ardent devotee of Lord Rama. He possesses various virtuous qualities and leads an army of monkey warriors to protect the people against all evils.

title: 10 Rupees
subTitle: Rambabu and Viswanatham, two friends, hatch a daring plan to escape their personal predicaments. However, things become complicated when their quick fix scheme backfires.

title: Annamalai
subTitle: Generations of rivalry come to light as two families fight for control of a revered temple while personal emotions complicate the path to peace.

title: Arasi
subTitle: Conflicting ideals and moral dilemmas challenge Senthamizharase and Selvi while they confront intricate family bonds and societal demands.

title: Piriyadha Varam Vendum
subTitle: A queen kills her son's lover who was a peasant and forces him to marry a princess of her choice. A million years later, they are reborn where the couple gets a chance to reunite.

title: Vaadi Rasathi
subTitle: Anjana Shankaran, an ordinary girl with extraordinary dreams aspires to become a District Collector and moreover, has the courage to claim the role of Chief Minister of Kerala one day.

title: Tenali Raman
subTitle: Tenali Raman, an advisor at the court of King Krishnadevaraya, uses his sharp presence of mind and wisdom to solve the difficult matters of the kingdom and its people daily.

title: Karna
subTitle: Karna, the son of the Sun God and Kunti, faces hardships from birth but strives to prove his worth. Overcoming challenges, he rises to become one of the most formidable archers and warriors in the Mahabharata.

title: Chanakya Thanthiram
subTitle: Chanakya, a philosopher and visionary strategist, joins hands with Chandragupta Maurya and becomes his chief advisor to save his empire.

title: Googly
subTitle: Sharath leads a carefree life until he meets Swathi at a college event. A friendship turns into a mutual attraction, but a small misunderstanding causes them to part ways.
